From fcde029e87d9c283352ea1ea8df4f14bf79d0dad Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 14 Jun 2026 14:38:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Clean up dead code and fix config regressions

- Remove orphaned hosts/desktop.nix (imported 7 nonexistent modules) and
  the now-unused modules/apps/ directory
- Remove stray committed files (y, nix-prefetch-url) and untrack .idea/;
  add a root .gitignore
- Restore Caddy CA trust (security.pki.certificates) into the active
  desktop host config; it was lost when desktop.nix was superseded
- Wire up `nix fmt` via a flake formatter output (alejandra), matching
  the README; fix stale modules/shared.nix reference in README
- Add automatic GC + auto-optimise-store to core/nix.nix
- Set home-manager.backupFileExtension so activation doesn't fail on
  pre-existing dotfiles
- Dedupe packages (git, rclone, steam) and tidy vulkan.nix; drop the
  redundant docker extraGroups entry on the desktop host
---
